Title: BPS Dyon in a Weak Electromagnetic Field: Equations of Motion and
  Radiation Fields
Authors: Dongsu Bak and Choonkyu Lee
Comments: 14 pages, Seoul National University preprint SNUTP 93-97
Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys. B424 (1994) 124-136
\\
  Dynamics of a BPS dyon in a weak, constant, electromagnetic field is studied
through a perturbative analysis of appropriate non-linear field equations. The
full Lorentz force law for a BPS dyon is established. Also derived are the
radiation fields accompanying the motion.
